#Command Briefing

$Stage Text:
 XSTR("The data from the Aethelgard has led us to a localized subspace instability on the edge of the Adhara system. Sensors indicate the GTSC Styx is anchored there.", -1)
$end_multi_text
$Ani Filename: <default>
+Wave Filename: none

$Stage Text:
 XSTR("However, the Styx is no longer a science vessel. It has been transformed into a staging ground for Shivan incursions. Bio-scans show no human life signs remaining.", -1)
$end_multi_text
$Ani Filename: <default>
+Wave Filename: none

$Stage Text:
 XSTR("High Command has authorized the total destruction of the Styx. We cannot allow this 'hive' to mature. Alpha and Beta will lead the assault.", -1)
$end_multi_text
$Ani Filename: <default>
+Wave Filename: none


#Briefing
$start_briefing
$num_stages: 3
$start_stage
$multi_text
 XSTR("The Styx is heavily defended by Shivan fighters. Gamma will provide interceptor cover. Alpha, you'll need to use your Hercules' heavy armor to get close to the Bio-Spires.", -1)
$end_multi_text
